_sText:
This is the 4th version of my map aim_rushmaze_texture which seems to be one of the most played on my server, whether it's because I include it in too many votes, it's coincidental, or people love it.

This version consists of several new easter eggs which I must give credit to souljah-uk^ for, I executed the plan but he came up with several of the ideas included in this new improved version.

I've updated the lighting slightly, made a few tweaks with the textures to make them look better and fixed some intersecting brushes in this version but the main focal point was the easter eggs.


<font size=3> <font color=red> Please, if you aren't going to test the map at least watch the video.

<object width="425" height="355"><param name="movie" value="http://www.youtube.com/v/WA_Th71Djnw"></param><param name="wmode" value="transparent"></param><embed src="http://www.youtube.com/v/WA_Th71Djnw" type="application/x-shockwave-flash" wmode="transparent" width="425" height="355"></embed></object>

Don't comment telling me to use real textures please, I attempted this and it looked horrid for this style.

<font size=5> Please don't just tell me it's good or bad, give me areas to improve in etc. And don't go ahead and give me all 10's unless you think it's absolutely perfect, take time and rate me truthfully.
